unittitle.value: Guide to the Polytechnic Marketing and Communications CD Image Collection

abstract.label: Abstract
abstract.value: This collection of compact discs (CDs) contains digital images of events and people related to Polytechnic. It was transferred to the Poly Archives from the Marketing and Communications Department in 2016.

p.value: The image CD collection was held in the Marketing and Communications Department offices until it was transferred to the Poly Archives on July 5, 2016.

The collection is comprised of compact discs (CDs) containing digital images of Polytechnic students, faculty, and events from 2002-2015. Some of these photographs were taken by the NYU Photo Bureau, some were taken by contracted photographers, and for some the original photographer is unknown.
